                    <p>
                        We automate time consuming tasks to free up
                        your resources and simplify
                        complex processes.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row mt-5">
                <div class="col-lg-4 shadow rounded-pill p-4" style=" background-color:#f2dff7; text-align:center">
                    <p>
                        <i class="bi bi-lightbulb-fill"></i> 
                        <b>Custom Solutions:</b>
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        We create applications,
                        automation, and data
                        analytics tools that
                        precisely fit your business
                        needs.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-4 p-4"></div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 shadow rounded-pill p-4" style="background-color:#cfcbf7; text-align:center">
                    <p>
