            <h3 class="text-center">Our Approach</h3><hr />
            <div class="row mt-5" style="text-align:center">
                <div class="col-lg-3 col-sm-6 shadow p-5">
                    <div><img src="~/Images/Services/Understanding.png" class="img-fluid h-50 w-50 m-3" /></div>
                    <p>
                        <b>Understanding:</b>
                    </p> 
                    <p>
                        We start by getting to know your
                        business and its challenges. We identify opportunities
                        where the Power Platform can make a difference.
                        </p> 
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-3 col-sm-6 shadow-lg p-5">
                    <div class="icon"><img src="~/images/services/DATA-DRIVEN DECISION-MAKING.png" class="img-fluid h-50 w-50 m-3" /></div>
                    <p>
                        <b>Design & Development:</b>
                    </p> 
                    <p>
                        We design and build
                        solutions that align with your goals, prioritizing
                        simplicity and user-friendliness.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-3 col-sm-6 shadow p-5">
                    <div class="icon"><img src="~/images/services/CUSTOMIZED SOLUTIONS.png" class="img-fluid h-50 w-50 m-3" /></div>
                    <p>
                        <b>Testing & Deployment:</b>
                    </p> 
                    <p>
                        We rigorously test our
