                <div class="col-lg-3 col-sm-6 shadow-lg p-5">
                    <div class="icon"><img src="~/images/services/END-TO-END SUPPORT.png" class="img-fluid h-50 w-50 m-3" /></div>
                    <p>
                        <b>Training & Support:</b></p> 
                    <p>We provide thorough training
                        and ongoing support to empower your team to make
                        the most of your new tools.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="container-fluid p-5" style="text-align:center">
            <p class="text-info h6">Let's Transform Your Business Together….</p>
            <p class="mt-3">
                At Voxtus, we believe in the power of the Microsoft Power Platform to make your
                business more efficient, data-driven, and productive. Partner with us to experience the
                benefits of tailored solutions.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-3 mb-3">
                Ready to get started? <a asp-controller="ContactUs" asp-action="Index" style="text-decoration:none">Contact us</a> today, and let's discuss how Voxtus can help you
